it is difficult to understand all at once but the Carta is a word that describes the spirit which composes all things. To put it another way, it is like a sort of elemental energy.<br>
<br>
もっと砕いて言うと普通「属性」と呼んでいるものにあたると考えると判りやすいです。<br>
